        <item>
            <title>Release 2.0.0</title>
            <description><![CDATA[
<b>New features:</b>
<ul>
  <li>Selection tool with Cut/Copy/Paste</li>
  <li>Line tool</li>
  <li>Text tool</li>
  <li>Path smoothing for pencil tool</li>
  <li>Tool options (palettes, brush sizes...) can now be customized</li>
  <li>New kinds of drawing surfaces:</li>
  <ul>
    <li>PDF presentations</li>
    <li>PDF reader</li>
    <li>Blank canvas</li>
  </ul>
  <li>Improved cursors when drawing</li>
  <li>Better support for macOS 11 and greater, and Apple Silicon</li>
</ul>
